summary:
The Mad God Devourer, Anivatri. 

 (E.E/U.O.M.G Concept) 

 One of the God's of Madness; The Mad God Of Consumption. - A being...
caption:
The Mad God Devourer, Anivatri.  (E.E/U.O.M.G Concept)

One of the God’s of Madness; The Mad God Of Consumption. - A being made up of multiple souls who were locked in a world between life and death, sometimes known as The Passing. As a punishment for a crime, a set of Elder Arch Wizards were put through a horrid trial where their bodies where destroyed and their souls were partially merged into one spirit form and then locked away within a helm meant to keep their partially merged spirit in place, and stored within The Passing. - Anivatri gained his continuously growing physical presence through a Wild Hunt style war against the Old Ones (old gods of EE/UOMG’s earth) By using his armies to help him destroy and consume the souls of the Old Ones using his Gauntlet. Allowing him to piece together his form over time and maintain a presence in the physical world.
